#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><title>
#: en/articles/lpi-101-intermediate-p3.xml:268
#, no-wrap
msgid "Finding the right man page"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><body><p>
#: en/articles/lpi-101-intermediate-p3.xml:272
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Sometimes it's hard to find the right man page for a given topic. In that case,\n"
"you might try using <c>man -k</c> to search the NAME section of the man pages.\n"
"Be warned that it's a substring search, so running something like <c>man -k\n"
"ls</c> will give you a lot of output! Here's an example using a more specific\n"
"query:\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Attribute 'caption' of: <guide><chapter><section><body><pre>
#: en/articles/lpi-101-intermediate-p3.xml:279
#, no-wrap
msgid "Searching man using man -k command"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><body><pre>
#: en/articles/lpi-101-intermediate-p3.xml:280
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ <i>man -k whatis</i>\n"
"apropos              (1)  - search the whatis database for strings\n"
"makewhatis           (8)  - Create the whatis database\n"
"whatis               (1)  - search the whatis database for complete words\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><title>
#: en/articles/lpi-101-intermediate-p3.xml:289
#, no-wrap
msgid "All about apropos"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><body><p>
#: en/articles/lpi-101-intermediate-p3.xml:293
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"The example on the previous panel brings up a few more points. First, the\n"
"<c>apropos</c> command is exactly equivalent to <c>man -k</c>. (In fact, I'll\n"
"let you in on a little secret. When you run <c>man -k</c>, it actually runs\n"
"<c>apropos</c> behind the scenes.) The second point is the <c>makewhatis</c>\n"
"command, which scans all the man pages on your Linux system and builds the\n"
"database for <c>whatis</c> and <c>apropos</c>. Usually this is run periodically\n"
"by root to keep the database updated:\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Attribute 'caption' of: <guide><chapter><section><body><pre>
#: en/articles/lpi-101-intermediate-p3.xml:302
#, no-wrap
msgid "Building whatis and apropos database"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><body><pre>
#: en/articles/lpi-101-intermediate-p3.xml:303
#, no-wrap
msgid "# <i>makewhatis</i>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><body><p>
#: en/articles/lpi-101-intermediate-p3.xml:307
#, no-wrap
msgid "For more information on \"man\" and friends, you should start with its man page:\n"
msgstr ""

